ates and local authorities it also provides specialized financial services such as factoring and lease finance asset management services which include savings solutions for individuals and investment solutions for institutional clients investor services such as custody services depositarytrustee services fund administration and issuer services and creditor insurance services as well as various private banking and wealth management services procurement process the company has a responsible supplier relations charter that it signed in  in order to keep a balanced relationship with its suppliers the charter is comprised of ten commitments related to responsible purchasing and lasting refashions as well as environmental impact issues financial equity and dependency risk it bytes • credit agricole recently opened its new data center which is comprised of  sites both located in chartres france  miles from paris and in which all data for credit agricole and its subsidiaries is stored ca immobilier… moreit bytes • credit agricole recently opened its new data center which is comprised of  sites both located in chartres france  miles from paris and in which all data for credit agricole and its subsidiaries is stored ca immobilier strategically developed the sites to maximize energy efficiency as well as promote green it • the company recently outsourced its decision support capabilities to teradata who integrated business intelligence systems supported a crm program with teradata active data warehouse and migrated data using teradata virtual storage sector industry financial banking financial financial services employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  management change company crédit agricole sa paris france change laurent darmon chief officer digital laurent darmon has been promoted to the position of chief officer digital darmon will be responsible for technical writing digital content marketing design and promotions  technology 